UNIVERSAL INC (1325)  said unconsolidated sales
in May fell 21.07% to NT$76,600,000 from NT$97,050,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  5/2012           5/2011
Sales             76,600           97,050    
YOY%             -21.07%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            352,832          494,499    
YOY%             -28.65% 
=================================================================
 